.SH 版本
.PP
v5.8.6 及以上版本
.SH 示例
.PP
\f[B]示例1：\f[] 对指定主机上的复制组重新选主
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.reelect({HostName: "sdbserver"})
{
  "MatchedNum": 3,
  "SucceedNum": 3,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 0
}
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]示例2：\f[] 对指定位置集的复制组重新选主
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.reelect({Location: "GuangZhou"})
{
  "MatchedNum": 4,
  "SucceedNum": 2,
  "IgnoredNum": 2,
  "FailedNum": 0
}
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]示例3：\f[] 结合域进行过滤后重新选主
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.reelect({HostName: "sdbserver", Domain: "mydomain"})
{
  "MatchedNum": 2,
  "SucceedNum": 1,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 1,
  "FailedGroups": ["group2"]
}
\f[]
.fi
.PP
\f[B]示例4：\f[] 使用多个域进行过滤
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> var dc = db.getDC()
> dc.reelect({Location: "GuangZhou", Domain: ["domain1", "domain2"]})
{
  "MatchedNum": 3,
  "SucceedNum": 3,
  "IgnoredNum": 0,
  "FailedNum": 0
}
\f[]
.fi
